{"tid":1528973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵跳閘教學（適合運動能力較差人士及面皮較薄人士）","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:27:08.000Z","uid":207191,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b346d2ee4720e8524ab6bdeae5b9151e4c11991d","tid":1528973,"uid":207191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"如果你地仲因為驚比人發現而唔跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者平時無做開運動 驚跳過去卡到會仆直變關家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁呢個方法啱晒你地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左現有嘅 㩒閘機跳過去 方法之外<br />\n仲可以跟人尾入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n教學：<br />\n<br />\n1. 搵一個新型閘機（紅色開關果啲）<br />\n2. 等有人差唔多入/出嘅時候 吊佢尾<br />\n3. 條友過左之後即刻9秒9沖過去！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果想逼真啲 可以鳩拎啲卡型物件 一野拍落個八達通位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  再沖過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想再以假亂真啲 可以再出口術 拍嘅同時大聲叫 &ldquo;嘟！&rdquo;一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過要小心啲 要把握時間快衝 如果唔係個紅色閘閂埋嚟夾到 會響幾聲（不過好快停）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果契弟走得麼嘅 響左都唔驚 直接跑走就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算你係邊方人仕 都可以放心跳閘<br />\n當懲罰港鐵又好 藍絲嘅 當幫政府慳返啲交通津貼又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要係咩？係幫自己慳錢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全民跳閘！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dafdbf078a8472316213c128308f89bc010024","tid":1528973,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7515a2a4479169a9cd21c96aa013da66ee6c41c5","tid":1528973,"uid":114121,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"拍嘅同時大聲叫 &ldquo;嘟！&rdquo;一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58e832fef2b979dc9ebaebfaa781fa3398fb7bf","tid":1528973,"uid":305631,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7515a2a4479169a9cd21c96aa013da66ee6c41c5","tid":1528973,"uid":114121,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"拍嘅同時大聲叫 &ldquo;嘟！&rdquo;一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"我建議手足扮閘 我弱智分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23eedd7060613656